</line>
<hr />
<line>Gumshoe:
I was in the hallway the whole time, but <textEffects>I didn't hear a single peep of a struggle</textEffects>.
</line>
<hr />
<line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(Was that statement really a lie...?)</textEffects>
</line><line>Badd:
