</line><line>Yew:
His motive for killing Rell? Like I would know.
</line><line>Edgeworth:
Hmph... If there was no clear motive for both of the murders... ...then I doubt this incident would've occurred. Wouldn't you agree?
</line><line>Yew:
..................
</line><line>Edgeworth:
