<line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(I wonder if that's really true... Is there <span style="color:#E16935">no one</textEffects> out there with a grudge against both men? I should take another hard look at the evidence for this morning's case. The second KG-8 Incident, as people are calling it, involving an Embassy staff member... ...and the two men who both wound up as suspects in the case... Is there someone else I'm overlooking who is somehow related to them?)</span>
</line>
